name: Awesomesimon29498.GitHub.io
body:
###Welcome to awesomesimon29498!
My name is Simon, and I like to redesign stuff so that they will be better. I also like to create stuff on my own, so don't be fooled.

### Redesign
Sometimes, when I feel that something doesn't quite fit my taste, I will redesign it and put it on my Github. For example, I have already redesigned one of my school's sites. 

### Creating
I don't just redesign stuff that other people made, I also create and redesign some of my own stuff! I will create software in multiple different languages such as HTML, Python, Java, JS, C++, and etc. 

### About me
I am a middle schooler at SFS, and currently, I am a beginner in programming, so don't judge me. 

### Support or Contact
You can contact me at twitter, facebook, and instagram. My username for all of these social media is awesomesimon29498. You can also contact me by email, which is "awesomesimon29498@gmail.com"
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
